# Dustify — soul-wallet app rules
# See root .cursorrules for complete platform rules
# This app is part of the Dustify Technologies Corp platform

## App: soul-wallet
## Framework: Next.js 14 (App Router) + TypeScript strict + Tailwind
## Auth: Uses SBT session from packages/security (Gatekeeper middleware)
## Design: Obsidian Sovereign (pure black + gold, Playfair + Cormorant + JetBrains Mono)
## Points: All DustMiles awards via 70/30 waterfall engine
## Security: Intelligence Guard middleware in src/middleware.ts

## NEVER:
- Use NextAuth (auth is FIDO2/WebAuthn + JWT only)
- Use any types (strict TypeScript always)
- Call blockchain directly from components (use packages/contracts)
- Hardcode API keys (use .env.local always)
- Use rounded-2xl or higher (max border-radius is 4px in Obsidian Sovereign)

